{"tid":2193770,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本YouTuber「跟親妹接吻」超開放","createTime":"2020-09-08T05:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T06:09:12.000Z","uid":137088,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cd345c831bae395d6b77be4994b5e18dbbb988ed","tid":2193770,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LK5GFiFOBT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLK5GFiFOBT8&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=5f64a1a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LK5GFiFOBT8</a>"},{"pid":"b4285e357f6d2b8c77230f485309ad5bdf2b962b","tid":2193770,"uid":137088,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:37:45.000Z","msg":"日本YouTuber「桐崎栄二.きりざきえいじ」擁有292萬名粉絲，而他在今年4月所上傳的一支影片卻在近日引起關注，他跟妹妹兩人輪流轉動輪盤，並且完成指定項目動作，而最令人感到驚訝的是，內容中竟然有「親親」這個選項，只見兩人一點也不避諱的在鏡頭前完成任務，讓許多網友紛紛懷疑「到底看到了甚麼」。<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，「桐崎栄二.きりざきえいじ」在4月時，上傳了一部名為「24小時與妹妹用輪盤決定生活，家庭崩潰開始&hellip;」的影片，內容即為自己跟妹妹輪流使用輪盤，並轉出接下來要做的事情，不過妹妹一開始就勁爆的轉到「接吻」的選項，兩人只隔著保鮮膜就真的親了上去。<br />\n<br />\n儘管事後妹妹崩潰的打了哥哥一巴掌，整個人滾到床上耍賴，不過短短幾秒的時間，卻帶給觀眾不小的衝擊。不僅僅只有這個影片，在其他「桐崎栄二.きりざきえいじ」的影片當中，兩人也時常做出親吻的行為，更出現躺在同一張床上睡覺等親密的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友在看完影片後紛紛表示，「這種想都想不到的事情，他們竟然做了&hellip;」、「怎麼有辦法辦到這樣的事！」、「以家人的關係來說，這樣的舉動好像有點過火了&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 百萬YouTuber「跟親妹接吻」超開放 24hrs挑戰網看傻：竟然做了 | ETtoday國際新聞 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200907/1803371.htm#ixzz6XPfBJPsf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200907%2F1803371.htm%23ixzz6XPfBJPsf&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=c42b6a38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200907/1803371.htm#ixzz6XPfBJPsf</a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"6740232a7cb3d15295084bf687d416afe391510c","tid":2193770,"uid":39274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"成日搵翻譯睇下佢講乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde66769c736378bf7bd047278e457d05d6089ff","tid":2193770,"uid":197782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"我又覺得冇乜問題喎"},{"pid":"d69e40b3b57a2915fb215858f48beebc734d4bbe","tid":2193770,"uid":330457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59eee04208602439b425407c96462cc49f93d9f","tid":2193770,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd1259bb586540e75f19625c208581f64669ef1","tid":2193770,"uid":286309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:41:37.000Z","msg":"之前都有個鬼佬 youtube8拍過<br />\n最後被人踢爆造假，條女唔家姐嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f03a5ec74f9cd4bf2af1ad50264cdb98a8bc139","tid":2193770,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"肯定已經扑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca96d78c1860c50d08b68c1fdc06ef8797ba09ec","tid":2193770,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"冇中譯